{"tid":2512812,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"以前D MK歌叫春歌詞真係好正","createTime":"2021-05-02T04:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T16:34:40.000Z","uid":61485,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b26005f8fa376402f594df38ff01e52adbb449","tid":2512812,"uid":61485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"很想要求你會三更半夜陪著我<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熱情淡了嘛 想抽身了嘛<br />\n聊電話也洩氣了嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何以 我變了你的 16號愛人<br />\n隨便 碰上哪個她 都比我更有趣吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平凡像我這一種 今天要認了命<br />\n才能學會不貪心 碰不到戀愛 也毫無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcaabb3a1faf654872fef86cc7fe1f49ec6f8f96","tid":2512812,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"搵返個男朋友就唔洗叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c27eae1ca337d343d035c045ff7631bc3670d4","tid":2512812,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"如果宜家出依d歌<br />\n屌 又係依d垃圾叫春狗血歌"},{"pid":"db39b5753a7b39862c912b521c685697ee080810","tid":2512812,"uid":61485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcaabb3a1faf654872fef86cc7fe1f49ec6f8f96","tid":2512812,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"搵返個男朋友就唔洗叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleadi